snippet.title: Tom Clancy’s Rainbow Six Siege – Steel Wave : Gameplay and Tips
snippet.description:
Ace and Melusi, the 2 new Operators from Operation Steel Wave are coming to the rescue! Discover the brand new House map, the abilities of our two fighters and everything that the season is bringing to the game.
